translated: Åkerblom, Lennart Sigfrid, dentist, Gothenburg, born on April 1, 1883 in Örgryte, Gothenburg and Bohus County, son of customs inspector Johan L. Å. and Amelie Neukammer. Married on April 24, 19xx to Maud Lamm. Education: Graduated from Gothenburg Higher Real School in 1904, dental studies completed in 1906, became a licensed dentist in 1908. Employed as a assistant clerk at the Customs Office in Gothenburg in 1904 and 1906. Started dental practice in Gothenburg in 1908.
